data.title: Wish we could have  stayed longer!
data.text: Only allowed about 45 minutes for a stop here..not nearly long enough! Very interesting, lots of good info, even a small..but nice, gift store.  Do yourself a favor...stop here!  Bring a group here, like I did!

data.title: Hidden Gem
data.text: I learned so much about the rich heritage of being Deaf in America.  So many famous people and wonderful unknown contributions to this country.  Everyone should go.  It's free.  Sweet little gift shop.  Super friendly people.
